$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
monitor_points

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
monitor_points -  This method prints out the health and gp points during combat, if the player so desires.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void monitor_points(object player,
int charge)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - the object recieving the monitor message
%^BOLD%^charge%^RESET%^ - non-zero to charge the player gp points for the message
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/health.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method prints out the health and gp points during combat,
if the player so desires. Moved to here from the combat effect.
.EP

